These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, peach, lettuce, radish
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indian, nigerian
1. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5
2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating radish is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
5. the brazilian is the person eating peach##1
6. the person eating lettuce is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Food      | radish  | blueberry | peach  | lettuce |
| Nationality   | indian | nigerian      | brazilian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, egyptian, italian, malaysian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, coffee, fanta
1. the egyptian is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | italian | egyptian   | australian |
| Beverage           | coffee      | sprite    | 7up | fanta      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, mouse, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, quad-bike, train
1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Pet        | hedgehog | dog | mouse     | pony |
| Transport   | car  | train   | quad-bike | bus    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is sailing##2
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | ice-hockey     | sailing    | handball       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, dutch, argentine, german
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western, zombie
1. the german is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the german is on the left or right of the argentine##3
3. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the dutch##3
6. the german is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Nationality          | argentine | german   | australian   | dutch    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | zombie | disaster | western |

