.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, paramedic, police-officer
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, car, tram, train
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
3. the person driving the train is between the police-officer and the person driving the tram##2
4. the paramedic is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | firefighter | police-officer | paramedic |
| Transport   | tram        | train     | van       | car   |

