.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, japanese, polish, brazilian
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, mechanic, scientist
1. the librarian is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the polish##3
4. the japanese is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | japanese     | brazilian | polish     | thai   |
| Job    | scientist | librarian  | mechanic | designer |

