.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, august, february
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, surfing, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5
4. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
5. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | march | august       | september   | february        |
| Sport      | surfing  | weightlifting | soccer | water-polo |

