.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, fishing, sudoku
City: hamburg, berlin, venice, miami
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
2. the person traveling to venice is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
5. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | board-games | drawing   | fishing | sudoku     |
| City   | berlin     | hamburg | venice  | miami |

