.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, horror, spy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, classical, d&b, trance
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
2. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
4. the person watching animation movies is the fan of d&b##1
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
6. the fan of classical is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror        | spy        | epic |
| Music-Genre         | d&b  | trance | reggae | classical |

