.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, woodworking, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, biathlon, rowing
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing | dancing | camping |
| Sport   | cricket     | rowing  | ice-hockey  | biathlon    |

