.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, april, august, march
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, canadian, mexican
1. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
2. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the american##5
3. the brazilian is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the mexican is the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday   | march  | january | april | august |
| Nationality   | canadian | american | brazilian   | mexican  |

