.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, puzzles, singing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, lily, marigold, zinnia
1. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
5. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | puzzles  | singing      | gardening |
| Flower     | marigold    | zinnia | lily | rose   |

