2. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
4. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
6. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking cola and the person who growsmarigold##2
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite  | fanta      | tea       |
| Flower   | rose | aconite | marigold | poppy |

