.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
4 different games are played: whist, monopoly, backgammon, go
1. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | milk     | soy-milk | cola     | hot-chocolate |
| Game   | backgammon | go  | whist | monopoly        |

