.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, hamster, mouse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, june, december, november
1. the owner of the bird is between the person who's birthday is in june and the owner of the goldfish##2
2. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | hamster   | mouse   | bird       | goldfish   |
| Birthday   | december | june | august | november |

