.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapes, strawberry, watermelon
House: townhouse, victorian, farmhouse, palace
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the palace house##1
3. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
4. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
6. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating watermelon and the townhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes     | watermelon | asparagus | strawberry |
| House   | farmhouse | palace | victorian      | townhouse        |

 